/******************************************************************
Stylesheet: 481px and Up Stylesheet

This stylesheet is loaded for larger devices. It's set to 
481px because at 480px it would load on a landscaped iPhone.
This isn't ideal because then you would be loading all those
extra styles on that same mobile connection. 

A word of warning. This size COULD be a larger mobile device,
so you still want to keep it pretty light and simply expand
upon your base.styl styles.

******************************************************************/
.center
	padding 0 0 15em
.home
	.center
		margin-top 0

.content-row-content
	column(12)
.grid-container .grid-item
	column(4)
	min-width 210px
	min-height 440px
	margin-bottom 20px
.single-episode .grid-container .grid-item
	min-height 310px
.sorting
	font-size 70%
/*********************
POSTS &: CONTENT STYLES
*********************/
.single
	.grid-container
		display block
	.back-btn
		display none

.single-post,
.page
	.archive-list
		width 100%
	.two-col
		column(6)
	.entry-content,
	.content-row-content
		img
			height auto
			clear none
			&.alignleft
				column(4)
				float left
				margin 0 (gutter-width) 1.5em 0
			&.alignright
				column(4)
				float right
				margin 0 0 1.5em (gutter-width)
			&.aligncenter
				margin .5em auto
				clear both

